56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的眼神和平時差別好大......你是感受到悲傷了嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "檢測到邊緣系統信號強烈波動。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......戴拉。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴拉蕾德？你又想起了她......難道九號裝置和弗蘭克斯主任的實驗也有聯繫？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動機，情感，而非邏輯聯繫。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默醫生，我能感受到，這是我們的選擇。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的......選擇？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼先生，假如我向你保證，我會盡一切努力讓所有錯誤都得到糾正，你是否願意暫時放過多蘿西·弗蘭克斯？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......赫默醫生，我們感激您一路上的幫助，更感激您為我們揭示了實驗的真相。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我願意相信您會站在我們這邊——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您真的能保證這個人不會重啟實驗嗎？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可萬一她真的這麼做了，我會替你解決她。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......實驗暫停，多蘿西沒有受傷，受試者們也正在逐漸恢復意識......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還有些不敢相信。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不必擔心，情緒起伏是正常現象。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬伊絲，你醒得太及時了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒見過奧利維亞那麼生氣......我真怕她會不管多蘿西。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還是搞不明白，你為什麼能聽到受試者們的聲音......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的意識是被多蘿西的“中樞”連在一起的，可你明明在外面，你到底是怎麼被捲進去的？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是說，九號裝置與“中樞”無關嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有效資訊不足，無法做出判斷。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，在夢醒的時候，我聽到了邁爾先生的聲音。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢醒的時候......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場發生在走廊上的衝突？就連之前的戰鬥都沒能起到作用，為什麼那會喚醒你？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好奇怪......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過事情解決了就好，多虧了奧利維亞。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默醫生做到了，符合預期。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在想想......她變化真大啊。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛認識她的時候，她還是個......唔，就大學裡很常見的那種好學生，文靜靦腆，不太愛說話。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以上描述與我的記憶相符。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛她逼問多蘿西又力保多蘿西的時候，我都快認不出她來了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就彷彿看到了......另一個人的影子。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏比卡研究員，你聯想的對象是否是塞雷婭主任？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你怎麼說出來了？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可別告訴奧利維亞我說了這樣的話啊！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默醫生並不會因此質疑你與她之間的友誼。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是作為她的朋友，我也不想讓她在這麼麻煩的時刻想起不太愉快的往事。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理解。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我也該繼續完成工作了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊......通訊還沒有恢復嗎？糟了，老闆那邊......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有姐姐，真不知道她會給我發多少消息......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗蘭克斯主任，麻煩你跟我一起離開實驗區。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......請等一下。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然實驗停了，他們一定不會讓這間實驗室留下。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一樣東西......我必須帶走。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......照片？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "照片上這些都是拓荒者......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這孩子是......你？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......赫默醫生，我對桑尼說的話，都是真心的。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的母親，我所有的親人......曾經都是拓荒者。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小就聽他們訴說自己的夢想，見過他們的奮鬥，也目睹過他們的掙扎。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是他們的付出令我有機會去追逐我自己的夢想。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我所擁有的幸運......大多數拓荒者都不可能擁有。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的家人們，他們現在......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他們之中的大多數都已經離開了我。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在我得到鑄鐵城理工大學的邀請，回城參加他們為極少數所謂“天才”舉辦的夏令營的時候......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場天災摧毀了我母親所在的臨時基地。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為一名研究者......曾經也是她的夢想。可她再也沒能等到我得到獎學金，被破格錄取的好消息。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一定非常難過......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默醫生，停下這個實驗，真的是正確的選擇嗎？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些拓荒者，那些被生活逼得走投無路的人們，他們或許明天就會遭遇厄運。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我本可以救他們......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不必像我的親人們一樣，絕望地被沙暴吞噬。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，為什麼要問我這樣的問題？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有我們的實驗，那個孩子在離開海頓一號實驗室之後根本活不了幾天。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們救活了她，我甚至讓你照顧她的起居，她不僅能享受衣食無憂的生活，還能為推動科學進步做貢獻——", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比在荒野上因為礦石病而悄無聲息死去的孩子們，她是多麼幸運啊。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我那麼信任你、器重你，你竟然......在這麼細枝末節的操作問題上指責我、指責科學本身？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個答案也不應該由我告訴你。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬伊絲提醒了我——", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便我永遠不會贊同你們......你的行為，我也不該用我的標準來評判一切。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被自我懷疑與不確定性折磨，難道不正是我們選擇的命運？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為研究者，我們只能自己去找答案。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g11_monitoringroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6, "crossfade": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都佈置好了嗎？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人已經進入基地，正在靠近實驗區。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，做好準備。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校先生，我明白現在已經有些遲了，請再給我一些時間......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......克魯尼，你沒有告訴我，有其他人進入了基地。", "name": "上校的聲音"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是指......那家醫藥企業？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不必擔心，他們是萊茵生命的合作方，我一定......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的保證沒有意義。", "name": "上校的聲音"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果——我們要的只有結果。", "name": "上校的聲音"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很抱歉，只是一點小小的延遲......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#5$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有結果的話，至少別給我們惹麻煩。", "name": "上校的聲音"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住這句話。", "name": "上校的聲音"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還要繼續行動嗎，斐爾迪南主任？", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我並不認為眼前還有其他選擇。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白了。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "替我接通特殊通訊頻道。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦......通訊？突然通了？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......埃琳娜。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了，我一直都想聯繫您，可惜連不上......您收到我的資訊了嗎？我把基地裡發生的事情都寫進了簡報裡。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西......弗蘭克斯主任的實驗出了點意外，不過沒關係，我和赫默研究員處理好了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有拓荒者，他們也被安撫好了，正在離開實驗區......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......您知道？這麼快......不愧是您。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做到了你該做的事，接下來會由其他人過來清理現場。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說防衛科的同事們？他們終於進來了嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......那我更放心了。我還在擔心實驗區儲存的那些遞質......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#10$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們知道該怎麼做，你可以撤出來了。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，我還是留下幫他們吧，除了多蘿西，基地裡只有我對實驗內容最熟悉。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，我此刻就在監控站，難道兩位主任還控制不了局面？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是這個意思......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就聽我的話，立刻撤出實驗基地。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能問一下為什麼嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別用這些沒有意義的提問浪費我的時間。馬上來監控室見我。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是，主任。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼問題嗎，烏比卡研究員？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任......斐爾迪南讓我立刻撤離。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撤離？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬伊絲，你先去通知奧利維亞吧，防衛科的人就要到了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢，要離開這裡嗎？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......主任的反應不太對勁。如果說......他並不知道多蘿西走到了哪一步，那他為什麼對實驗出的狀況毫不關心？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g11_monitoringroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南主任，埃琳娜小姐並未離開實驗區。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "